data.meta_description:
T.R. Knight aka Dr. George O’Malley is our very special guest resident in the O.R. this week

He reveals an off screen surprise during his characters final moments on Greys Anatomy.

Plus we reflect on the aftermath of last week’s “Truth or Drink” game and answer some bonus questions.
